tspan.tspan: Thesis: Researched and worked on a state of the art Nonlinear Model Predictive Controller
to control a group of heterogeneous UAVs equiped with various sensors to collaboratively
measure the state of a target object using a cooperative Kalman filter. The controller is built
on the Genome framework in Python and C++. The controller uses a model that captures the
full nonlinear dynamics of the UAVs and outputs low-level actuator inputs for each of the

text.tspan: UAV rotors.
